  <name>Saturn</name>
  <summary>Browse and manage Flatpak apps</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      Saturn is a Flatpak application launcher and manager for GNOME. It lets you
      browse installed Flatpak applications, view application details, and launch
      apps from a single interface.
    </p>
    <p>
      Built with GTK4 and libadwaita, Saturn follows GNOME design conventions and
      integrates with the Flatpak system to provide a unified view of your installed
      applications across both system and user installations.
    </p>
  </description>

  <developer id="io.github.kolunmi">
    <name>Eva M</name>
  </developer>

